db:article.db:para: The Tango Desktop Project exists to help create a consistent graphical user interface experience for free and Open Source software.

The sources can be found in qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-few-clouds.png, qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-overcast.png, qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-showers.png, qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-storm.png, qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-snow.png, and qtpositioning/examples/positioning/weatherinfo/icons/weather-showers-scattered.png.
